OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to damaging property
OL,4,Cafter house explosion hospitalised man
OL,6,FCredit: Pictures from Ashley Kirk
OL,8,FA man is facing prison after pleading
OL,9,Fguilty to an explosion which destroyed
OL,10,Fa terraced house in Derby and left
OL,11,Fanother man hospitalised.
OL,13,FEmergency services were called to
OL,14,Freports of a suspected gas explosion
OL,15,Fin Eden Street in the Alvaston area of
OL,16,Fthe city at around 7.24pm on June 10
OL,17,Flast year.
