OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to damaging property
OL,4,Cafter house explosion hospitalised man
OL,6,FPaul Solway, 57, admitted six counts
OL,7,Fof damaging property being reckless as
OL,8,Fto whether life was endangered,
OL,9,Frelating to six different properties
OL,10,Fat Derby Crown Court.
OL,12,FJudge Shaun Smith KC told the
OL,13,Fdefendant his sentence is "going to be
OL,14,Fimprisonment".
OL,16,FDoorbell footage captured the house
OL,17,Fexplosion on Eden Street
OL,19,FJurors who had been selected to try
OL,20,Fthe case on Monday were told they are
OL,21,Fno longer needed for the trial.
