OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to damaging property
OL,4,Cafter house explosion hospitalised man
OL,6,FThe judge told the jury: "The
OL,7,Fprosecution case is that Mr Solway is
OL,8,Fresponsible for that explosion.
OL,10,F"It was going to be suggested it was a
OL,11,Fgas leak ` he accepts now he's
OL,12,Fcriminally responsible."
OL,14,FSolway, of no fixed address, who stood
OL,15,Fin the dock wearing a blue top with a
OL,16,Fgrey sweatshirt draped over his
OL,17,Fshoulders and a bandage on his arm,
OL,18,Fwas told he will be sentenced on April
OL,19,F8.
